'''''High Seize''''' is a [[turn-based tactics]] [[video game]] for the [[Nokia]] [[N-Gage (device)|N-Gage]], published by [[Nokia]] and developed by [[RedLynx]], released in late 2005.
==Story== A retired navy captain is forced return to his swashbuckling days, as his father is kidnapped by a notorious pirate. As events unfolds, the captain has to hunt for mythical treasures and take on the most feared of all pirates, Black Barlow.
==Features== ''High Seize'' can be played both as a [[single-player]] game, and in a [[multi-player]] mode, using either hot-seat, [[N-Gage Arena]] or a local [[Bluetooth]] connection.
